 We find that 
\begin_inset Formula $a_{1}=623.04$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $a_{2}=9.03\times10^{18}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $b=1.656\times10^{-15}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $d=0.869$
\end_inset

, and 
\begin_inset Formula $e=-17.855$
